name: "The sun rises in the east"
description: She pretends to be Yayoi Kusama for a day. She was whispering: "Well; after all, the moon is a polkadot, the sun is a polkadot and then, the earth where we live is also a polkadot; you can find them in the form of the eternally mysterious cosmos too. through them, I see the philosophy of life."
